<p>in my code in a place where a call is made to <code>CoCreateInstance(...)</code> with a first parameter <code>CLSID_StdGlobalInterfaceTable</code>, I get an undeclared identifier error in these two functions in <code>atlbase.h</code>:</p>  <pre><code>HRESULT GetGITPtr(_Deref_out_ IGlobalInterfaceTable** ppGIT)  HRESULT AtlGetGITPtr(_Deref_out_ IGlobalInterfaceTable** ppGIT) </code></pre>  <p>Here is the order that I make my includes in:</p>  <pre><code>#include &lt;objidl.h&gt; #include &lt;Guiddef.h&gt; DEFINE_GUID(GUID_NULL, 0x00000000L, 0x0000, 0x0000, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00); #include &lt;atlbase.h&gt; #include &lt;atlcom.h&gt; #include &lt;Shobjidl.h&gt; #include &lt;string&gt; </code></pre>  <p>I didn't have GUID_NULL either, so I defined it myself.</p>